        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1916479209" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3191850425672922752">What a nice book! <br/><br/>It&apos;s supposedly a fairy-tale retelling of Cinderella, but there are only a few Cinderella shout-outs such as sleeping by the fireplace and an unpleasant stepmother. For all intents and purposes, this book is an original peasant-princess story. It&apos;s a kids&apos; book, so it&apos;s fast and short, but I thoroughly enjoyed it.<br/><br/>The only <i>real</i> issue is that I&apos;m no fan of the cover, and the title is pretty meaningless and irrelevant. I would have gotten around to reading it way before now if the</span>
  <span id="freeText3191850425672922752" style="display:none">What a nice book! <br /><br />It's supposedly a fairy-tale retelling of Cinderella, but there are only a few Cinderella shout-outs such as sleeping by the fireplace and an unpleasant stepmother. For all intents and purposes, this book is an original peasant-princess story. It's a kids' book, so it's fast and short, but I thoroughly enjoyed it.<br /><br />The only <i>real</i> issue is that I'm no fan of the cover, and the title is pretty meaningless and irrelevant. I would have gotten around to reading it way before now if these factors hadn't held me back.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3191850425672922752" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
